/div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001183_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001183_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001183.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001183-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text according to Kaibel in IG</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Castelli 1769 cl.10 no.40 = Castelli (1784) cl.10 no.45 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a></li><li> Franz 1853 5603 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">361</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.527 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
